{"tid":149700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有好多唔同類型既朋友","createTime":"2017-03-09T12:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T13:43:25.000Z","uid":31112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f23391e02f64a661a89212d55857f5d51402e12d","tid":149700,"uid":31112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"啲人成日話睇你識咩朋友就知你係一個點既人<br />\n可能係相同興趣、相似衣著品味、家景相近<br />\n我觀察到其他人識朋友果陣都會咁歸類<br />\n但我唔會咁<br />\n我係睇下一個人有咩優點<br />\n然後會配合果個人<br />\n姐係如果佢睇落水木"},{"pid":"de5497ff9be130ec65166a7bce370362fa42a010","tid":149700,"uid":31112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T12:49:39.000Z","msg":"未打完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果佢睇落個look 7下7下咁<br />\n但講野好有見地 又有性格既話<br />\n我都會同佢玩得埋<br />\n但我見身邊啲人唔係咁<br />\n其實係味好少係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f454cf09fa0c75ab13a18328107c905dc27563a","tid":149700,"uid":31112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T12:58:41.000Z","msg":"開左係吹水台冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a21f67ac2dfc76eb6512292fe4f4c1536529d73","tid":149700,"uid":47566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"幫你推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f283103eab13454fdaf7f3b4c38d7783f7943887","tid":149700,"uid":31112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫你推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}